        },
        {
            "id": 1,
            "parent": 13,
            "text": "Plant artificial micro - RNAs ( amiRs ) have been engineered",
            "relation": "BACKGROUND"
        },
        {
            "id": 2,
            "parent": 1,
            "text": "to target viral genomes",
            "relation": "ENABLEMENT"
        },
        {
            "id": 3,
            "parent": 2,
            "text": "and induce their degradation . <S>",
            "relation": "JOINT"
        },
        {
            "id": 4,
            "parent": 1,
            "text": "However , the exceptional evolutionary plasticity of RNA viruses threatens the durability of the resistance",
            "relation": "COMPARISON"
        },
        {
            "id": 5,
            "parent": 4,
            "text": "conferred by these amiRs . <S>",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 6,
            "parent": 4,
            "text": "It has recently been shown that viral populations",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 7,
            "parent": 6,
            "text": "not experiencing strong selective pressure from an antiviral amiR",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 8,
            "parent": 6,
            "text": "may already contain enough genetic variability in the target sequence",
            "relation": "SAME-UNIT"
        },
        {
            "id": 9,
            "parent": 8,
            "text": "to escape plant resistance in an almost deterministic manner . <S>",
            "relation": "ENABLEMENT"
        },
        {
            "id": 10,
            "parent": 6,
            "text": "Furthermore , it has also been shown that viral populations",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 11,
            "parent": 10,
            "text": "exposed to subinhibitory concentrations of the antiviral amiR",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 12,
            "parent": 10,
            "text": "speed up this process . <S>",
            "relation": "SAME-UNIT"
        },
        {
            "id": 13,
            "parent": 0,
            "text": "In this article , we have characterized the molecular evolutionary dynamics of an amiR target sequence in a viral genome under both conditions . <S>",
            "relation": "ROOT"
        },
        {
            "id": 14,
            "parent": 13,
            "text": "The use of Illumina ultradeep sequencing has allowed us to identify virus sequence variants at frequencies as low as 2 \u00c2 10 \u00c06 and to track their variation in time",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 15,
            "parent": 14,
            "text": "before and after the viral population was able of successfully infecting plants fully resistant to the ancestral virus . <S>",
            "relation": "TEMPORAL"
        },
        {
            "id": 16,
            "parent": 17,
            "text": "We found",
            "relation": "ATTRIBUTION"
        },
        {
            "id": 17,
            "parent": 13,
            "text": "that every site in the amiR - target sequence of the viral genome presented variation",
            "relation": "FINDINGS"
        },
        {
            "id": 18,
            "parent": 17,
            "text": "and that the variant",
            "relation": "JOINT"
        },
        {
            "id": 19,
            "parent": 18,
            "text": "that eventually broke resistance",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 20,
            "parent": 18,
            "text": "was sampled among the many coexisting ones . <S>",
            "relation": "SAME-UNIT"
        },
        {
            "id": 21,
            "parent": 17,
            "text": "In this system , viral evolution in fully susceptible plants results from an equilibrium between mutation and genetic drift ,",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 22,
            "parent": 21,
            "text": "whereas evolution in partially resistant plants originates from more complex dynamics",
            "relation": "COMPARISON"
        },
        {
            "id": 23,
            "parent": 22,
            "text": "involving mutation , selection , and drift . <S> <P>",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        }
    ]
}